{"type":"message","id":"7a9beff7","parentId":"401f91fb","timestamp":"2026-03-15T12:46:44.430Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要把电脑美化成 Notion 风格。这是一个桌面美化/定制的请求。\n\n让我先了解一下用户的系统环境：\n- Windows 10/11 (从 runtime 信息看是 Windows NT 10.0.26200)\n\nNotion 风格通常意味着：\n- 干净、简约的设计\n- 黑白或柔和的配色\n- 无边框、圆角元素\n- 清晰的排版\n\n对于 Windows 桌面美化，可以考虑：\n1. 壁纸选择 - Notion 风格的简约壁纸\n2. 桌面小部件 - 使用 Rainmeter 或类似工具\n3. 图标美化\n4. 任务栏定制\n5. 窗口主题\n\n我觉得这个任务我可以通过一些 web_search 来找一些资源和方案，然后给用户提供具体的建议。\n\n让我搜索一下相关的美化方案。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，想要 Notion 风格的桌面！那种干净、极简、黑白的调调。\n\n让我先搜一下最新的 Windows Notion 风格美化方案："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf188d8f1aa76f89db88a3ae53cf2","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"Windows desktop Notion style theme customization 2024 2025","count":8}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf188db122c82f3dd140a7fc3a27e","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"Rainmeter Notion style skin minimal","count":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":185,"output":451,"cacheRead":15104,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15740,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773578796772}}
{"type":"message","id":"a1f65a0a","parentId":"7a9beff7","timestamp":"2026-03-15T12:46:44.453Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019cf188d8f1aa76f89db88a3ae53cf2","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"error\": \"missing_brave_api_key\",\n  \"message\": \"web_search (brave) needs a Brave Search API key. Run `openclaw configure --section web` to store it, or set BRAVE_API_KEY in the Gateway environment.\",\n  \"docs\": \"https://docs.openclaw.ai/tools/web\"\n}"}],"details":{"error":"missing_brave_api_key","message":"web_search (brave) needs a Brave Search API key. Run `openclaw configure --section web` to store it, or set BRAVE_API_KEY in the Gateway environment.","docs":"https://docs.openclaw.ai/tools/web"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773578804451}}
{"type":"message","id":"a284448f","parentId":"a1f65a0a","timestamp":"2026-03-15T12:46:44.454Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019cf188db122c82f3dd140a7fc3a27e","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"error\": \"missing_brave_api_key\",\n  \"message\": \"web_search (brave) needs a Brave Search API key. Run `openclaw configure --section web` to store it, or set BRAVE_API_KEY in the Gateway environment.\",\n  \"docs\": \"https://docs.openclaw.ai/tools/web\"\n}"}],"details":{"error":"missing_brave_api_key","message":"web_search (brave) needs a Brave Search API key. Run `openclaw configure --section web` to store it, or set BRAVE_API_KEY in the Gateway environment.","docs":"https://docs.openclaw.ai/tools/web"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773578804452}}
{"type":"message","id":"6208f1c0","parentId":"a284448f","timestamp":"2026-03-15T12:46:59.304Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"网络搜索不可用，没有配置 Brave API key。没关系，我可以基于我的知识给用户提供一些建议。\n\n让我给用户一个完整的 Notion 风格美化方案：\n\n**Notion 风格特点：**\n- 极简、干净\n- 黑白灰为主，配合柔和的点缀色\n- 大量留白\n- 清晰的字体和层级\n- 圆角元素\n\n**Windows 美化方案：**\n\n1. **壁纸** - 简约的 Notion 风格壁纸\n2. **Rainmeter** - 打造 Notion 风格的小部件\n3. **图标** - 统一的简约图标包\n4. **任务栏** - 透明化或隐藏\n5. **鼠标指针** - 简约风格\n\n让我给用户一个详细的指南。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"网络搜索暂时不可用，但我可以给你一套完整的 Notion 风格美化方案！\n\n---\n\n## 🖤 Notion 风格 Windows 美化指南\n\n### 1. 壁纸\n简约、高留白是关键：\n- 纯色壁纸（奶白 #FAFAF9 或深黑 #191919）\n- 极简几何线条\n- 黑白摄影作品\n- 下载站：[Wallhaven](https://wallhaven.cc) 搜索 \"minimal\" 或 \"notion\"\n\n### 2. Rainmeter（桌面小部件）\n打造类似 Notion 侧边栏的效果：\n- **时间/日期** - 大字体，左上角\n- **待办清单** - 可勾选的任务列表\n- **快捷方式** - Application 快捷启动\n- **天气** - 简约天气模块\n\n推荐皮肤：\n- **Monstercat** - 极简风格\n- **Lano** - 圆角卡片设计\n- 自己用代码手写一个 Notion 风格的 ini\n\n### 3. 图标包\n统一风格：\n- **Papirus** - 圆角简约\n- **WhiteSur** - macOS 风格\n- **Nord** - 柔和配色\n\n### 4. 任务栏美化\n- **TranslucentTB** - 透明任务栏\n- 设置：居中图标、隐藏搜索框、精简图标\n- Windows 11 原生支持任务栏美化\n\n### 5. 窗口主题\n- 用 **Windhawk** 或 **SecureUXTheme** 应用自定义主题\n- 选一个灰白色调的主题\n\n---\n\n**你想要哪种程度的改造？**\n- 🪶 轻量级（只换壁纸 + Rainmeter）\n- 🔧 中等（加图标包 + 任务栏透明）\n- 🏗️ 完整（全部来一遍，包括窗口主题）\n\n告诉我你的选择，我可以帮你一步步配置！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":476,"output":783,"cacheRead":15232,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16491,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773578804455}}
