{"type":"message","id":"ecee7208","parentId":"78f4b9e7","timestamp":"2026-03-15T12:48:30.441Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，Windows 10 Pro for Workstations，版本 25H2，Build 26200。这是一个比较新的版本。\n\n现在我来为用户制定完整的美化计划并执行：\n\n1. 创建一个美化文件夹来存放下载的东西\n2. 下载壁纸\n3. 检查/安装 Rainmeter\n4. 检查/安装 TranslucentTB\n5. 创建自定义的 Notion 风格 Rainmeter 皮肤\n6. 配置任务栏\n\n让我开始吧。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Windows 10 Pro 25H2，很新的系统。开始完整美化！\n\n---\n\n## 🛠️ 第一步：准备工作"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf18a6853e5f915e52372251ab1f9","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 创建美化工作目录\n$workspace = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\"\nif (-not (Test-Path $workspace)) { New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $workspace -Force }\nWrite-Host \"工作目录: $workspace\"\n\n# 检查已安装的美化软件\nWrite-Host \"`n=== 已安装软件检查 ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n$apps = @(\"Rainmeter\", \"TranslucentTB\")\nforeach ($app in $apps) {\n    $installed = Get-ItemProperty \"HKLM:\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Uninstall\\*\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Where-Object { $_.DisplayName -like \"*$app*\" }\n    if ($installed) {\n        Write-Host \"[✓] $app 已安装\" -ForegroundColor Green\n    } else {\n        Write-Host \"[✗] $app 未安装\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n    }\n}\n\n# 检查 winget 是否可用\n$winget = Get-Command winget -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nif ($winget) {\n    Write-Host \"`n[✓] winget 可用，将用于安装软件\" -ForegroundColor Green\n} else {\n    Write-Host \"`n[✗] winget 不可用\" -ForegroundColor Red\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":189,"output":524,"cacheRead":16128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16841,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773578900979}}
