{"type":"message","id":"c6a8d6cb","parentId":"deb867ce","timestamp":"2026-03-15T12:51:18.933Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"GitHub 下载超时了。可能是网络问题。让我尝试使用镜像站点或者检查是否已经有这些软件。\n\n或者，我可以让用户手动下载这些文件，同时我先准备好配置文件。\n\n另一种方案是使用 PowerShell 静默安装参数，如果用户已经有安装包的话。\n\n让我先创建一个完整的美化包，包括脚本来下载和安装。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"网络连接超时。让我换个方式 - 先创建完整的配置文件，你手动运行安装脚本："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf18cffe1c49cad32982bfdfd6db8","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 创建完整的 Notion 风格主题包\n$themeDir = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\"\n\n# 1. 创建壁纸目录\n$wallpaperDir = \"$themeDir\\wallpapers\"\nNew-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $wallpaperDir -Force | Out-Null\n\n# 2. 创建 Rainmeter 皮肤目录\n$skinDir = \"$themeDir\\rainmeter-skins\\NotionStyle\"\nNew-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $skinDir -Force | Out-Null\n\nWrite-Host \"[✓] 目录结构创建完成\" -ForegroundColor Green\nWrite-Host \"  $themeDir\"\nWrite-Host \"  ├─ wallpapers/\"\nWrite-Host \"  └─ rainmeter-skins/NotionStyle/\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":426,"output":342,"cacheRead":19200,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19968,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773579070378}}
