{"type":"message","id":"61f4eade","parentId":"15fda207","timestamp":"2026-03-15T12:51:52.081Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，目录创建成功。现在我需要创建：\n1. 一个 Notion 风格的 Rainmeter 皮肤（包含时间、日期、待办事项、快捷方式等）\n2. 一个纯色壁纸\n3. 安装脚本\n\n让我一步步创建这些文件。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在创建 Notion 风格的 Rainmeter 皮肤："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf18d1defa83f4d3cb42619b80850","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\rainmeter-skins\\NotionStyle\\NotionStyle.ini","content":"; ============================================\n; Notion Style Rainmeter Skin\n; 极简 · 黑白 · 高效\n; ============================================\n\n[Rainmeter]\nUpdate=1000\nAccurateText=1\nDynamicWindowSize=1\n\n[Variables]\n; === 颜色配置 ===\nTextColor=#FAFAF9\nTextDark=#191919\nAccentColor=#2EAADC\nFontSize_Small=10\nFontSize_Medium=14\nFontSize_Large=48\nFontSize_Title=24\nFontName=Microsoft YaHei UI\n\n; === 背景 ===\n[Background]\nMeter=Shape\nShape=Rectangle 0,0,350,0,8 | Fill #19191910 | Stroke 0\n\n; ============================================\n; 时间模块\n; ============================================\n[Time]\nMeter=String\nX=0\nY=0\nFontFace=#FontName#\nFontSize=#FontSize_Large#\nFontColor=#TextColor#\nStringAlign=Left\nAntiAlias=1\nMeasureName=MeasureTime\n\n[MeasureTime]\nMeasure=Time\nFormat=%H:%M\n\n[Date]\nMeter=String\nX=0\nY=56\nFontFace=#FontName#\nFontSize=#FontSize_Medium#\nFontColor=#TextColor#\nStringAlign=Left\nAntiAlias=1\nMeasureName=MeasureDate\n\n[MeasureDate]\nMeasure=Time\nFormat=%A, %B %d\n\n[WeekProgress]\nMeter=String\nX=0\nY=80\nFontFace=#FontName#\nFontSize=#FontSize_Small#\nFontColor=#TextColor#80\nStringAlign=Left\nAntiAlias=1\nMeasureName=MeasureWeekProgress\n\n[MeasureWeekProgress]\nMeasure=Time\nFormat=Week %W\n\n; ============================================\n; 分隔线\n; ============================================\n[Divider1]\nMeter=Shape\nShape=Line 0,0,200,0 | Stroke #TextColor#30, 1\nX=0\nY=110\n\n; ============================================\n; 待办事项\n; ============================================\n[TodoTitle]\nMeter=String\nX=0\nY=130\nFontFace=#FontName#\nFontSize=#FontSize_Title#\nFontColor=#TextColor#\nFontWeight=600\nStringAlign=Left\nAntiAlias=1\nText=📋 Todo\n\n[Todo1]\nMeter=String\nX=10\nY=165\nFontFace=#FontName#\nFontSize=#FontSize_Medium#\nFontColor=#TextColor#\nStringAlign=Left\nAntiAlias=1\nText=☐ 整理桌面文件\n\n[Todo1Click]\nMeter=String\nX=0\nY=165\nW=300\nH=25\nMouseOverAction=[!SetOption Todo1 FontColor \"#AccentColor\"][!Update]\nMouseLeaveAction=[!SetOption Todo1 FontColor \"#TextColor\"][!Update]\nLeftMouseUpAction=[!ToggleMeter Todo1Done][!ToggleMeter Todo1]\nDynamicVariables=1\n\n[Todo1Done]\nMeter=String\nX=10\nY=165\nFontFace=#FontName#\nFontSize=#FontSize_Medium#\nFontColor=#TextColor#60\nStringAlign=Left\nAntiAlias=1\nText=☑ 整理桌面文件\nHidden=1\n\n[Todo2]\nMeter=String\nX=10\nY=190\nFontFace=#FontName#\nFontSize=#FontSize_Medium#\nFontColor=#TextColor#\nStringAlign=Left\nAntiAlias=1\nText=☐ 阅读技术文档\n\n[Todo3]\nMeter=String\nX=10\nY=215\nFontFace=#FontName#\nFontSize=#FontSize_Medium#\nFontColor=#TextColor#\nStringAlign=Left\nAntiAlias=1\nText=☐ 项目进度更新\n\n[Todo4]\nMeter=String\nX=10\nY=240\nFontFace=#FontName#\nFontSize=#FontSize_Medium#\nFontColor=#TextColor#a0\nStringAlign=Left\nAntiAlias=1\nText=☐ + 添加新任务...\n\n; ============================================\n; 分隔线\n; ============================================\n[Divider2]\nMeter=Shape\nShape=Line 0,0,200,0 | Stroke #TextColor#30, 1\nX=0\nY=275\n\n; ============================================\n; 快捷方式\n; ============================================\n[QuickLinksTitle]\nMeter=String\nX=0\nY=290\nFontFace=#FontName#\nFontSize=#FontSize_Title#\nFontColor=#TextColor#\nFontWeight=600\nStringAlign=Left\nAntiAlias=1\nText=⚡ Quick Links\n\n[LinkChrome]\nMeter=String\nX=10\nY=325\nFontFace=#FontName#\nFontSize=#FontSize_Medium#\nFontColor=#TextColor#\nStringAlign=Left\nAntiAlias=1\nText=🌐 Chrome\nLeftMouseUpAction=[\"chrome.exe\"]\n\n[LinkVSCode]\nMeter=String\nX=10\nY=350\nFontFace=#FontName#\nFontSize=#FontSize_Medium#\nFontColor=#TextColor#\nStringAlign=Left\nAntiAlias=1\nText=💻 VS Code\nLeftMouseUpAction=[\"code\"]\n\n[LinkTerminal]\nMeter=String\nX=10\nY=375\nFontFace=#FontName#\nFontSize=#FontSize_Medium#\nFontColor=#TextColor#\nStringAlign=Left\nAntiAlias=1\nText> Terminal\nLeftMouseUpAction=[\"wt\"]\n\n[LinkExplorer]\nMeter=String\nX=10\nY=400\nFontFace=#FontName#\nFontSize=#FontSize_Medium#\nFontColor=#TextColor#\nStringAlign=Left\nAntiAlias=1\nText=📁 Explorer\nLeftMouseUpAction=[\"explorer.exe\"]\n\n; ============================================\n; 名言区域 (可自定义)\n; ============================================\n[Divider3]\nMeter=Shape\nShape=Line 0,0,200,0 | Stroke #TextColor#30, 1\nX=0\nY=435\n\n[Quote]\nMeter=String\nX=0\nY=455\nW=300\nH=60\nFontFace=#FontName#\nFontSize=#FontSize_Small#\nFontColor=#TextColor#80\nStringAlign=Left\nAntiAlias=1\nText=\"The only way to do great work#CRLF#is to love what you do.\"\nClipString=2\n\n[QuoteAuthor]\nMeter=String\nX=0\nY=510\nFontFace=#FontName#\nFontSize=#FontSize_Small#\nFontColor=#TextColor#50\nStringAlign=Left\nAntiAlias=1\nText=— Steve Jobs\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":740,"output":1506,"cacheRead":19200,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21446,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773579080009}}
