{"type":"message","id":"defbab9a","parentId":"d0c1d179","timestamp":"2026-03-15T12:54:25.187Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了！壁纸已经设置成功。现在需要帮用户下载 Rainmeter 和 TranslucentTB。由于网络问题，让我创建一个更好的下载脚本并提供备用的手动下载链接。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"壁纸已设置！现在下载 Rainmeter 和 TranslucentTB："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf18fc96decc4937606e59abfd60b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 尝试使用不同的方式下载软件\n$themeDir = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\"\n\nWrite-Host \"Downloading Rainmeter...\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n$rainmeterUrl = \"https://github.com/rainmeter/rainmeter/releases/download/v4.5.18.3762/Rainmeter-4.5.18.3762.exe\"\n$rainmeterPath = \"$themeDir\\rainmeter-installer.exe\"\n\n# 使用 .NET WebClient (更快)\n$webClient = New-Object System.Net.WebClient\n$webClient.Headers.Add(\"User-Agent\", \"Mozilla/5.0\")\n\ntry {\n    $webClient.DownloadFile($rainmeterUrl, $rainmeterPath)\n    Write-Host \"[OK] Rainmeter downloaded: $rainmeterPath\" -ForegroundColor Green\n} catch {\n    Write-Host \"[SKIP] Network issue, please download manually:\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n    Write-Host \"       https://www.rainmeter.net/\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n}\n\nWrite-Host \"`nDownloading TranslucentTB...\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n$tbUrl = \"https://github.com/TranslucentTB/TranslucentTB/releases/download/2024.1/TranslucentTB.Setup.exe\"\n$tbPath = \"$themeDir\\translucenttb-installer.exe\"\n\ntry {\n    $webClient.DownloadFile($tbUrl, $tbPath)\n    Write-Host \"[OK] TranslucentTB downloaded: $tbPath\" -ForegroundColor Green\n} catch {\n    Write-Host \"[SKIP] Network issue, please download manually:\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n    Write-Host \"       https://github.com/TranslucentTB/TranslucentTB/releases\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n}","timeout":180}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":415,"output":454,"cacheRead":27136,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28005,"