{"type":"message","id":"87d1d147","parentId":"61859c1b","timestamp":"2026-03-15T12:54:38.488Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"网络问题导致无法自动下载。让我创建一个完整的安装指导文件，并检查文件完整性。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"网络原因无法自动下载。让我检查已创建的文件："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf1900974e34560a00b991cd4dd8b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查已创建的所有文件\n$themeDir = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\"\n\nWrite-Host \"=== Notion Theme Package ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host \"\"\n\nGet-ChildItem -Path $themeDir -Recurse | ForEach-Object {\n    if ($_.PSIsContainer) {\n        Write-Host \"📁 $($_.Name)\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n    } else {\n        $size = [math]::Round($_.Length / 1KB, 1)\n        Write-Host \"   📄 $($_.Name) ($size KB)\" -ForegroundColor White\n    }\n}\n\nWrite-Host \"\"\nWrite-Host \"Total size:\" -NoNewline\n$totalSize = (Get-ChildItem -Path $themeDir -Recurse -File | Measure-Object -Property Length -Sum).Sum\nWrite-Host \" $([math]::Round($totalSize / 1MB, 2)) MB\" -ForegroundColor Green"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":1081,"output":272,"cacheRead":26944,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28297,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773579270642}}
{"type":"message","id":"650a0999","parentId":"87d1d147","timestamp":"2026-03-15T12:54:39.541Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019cf1900974e34560a00b991cd4dd8b","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== Notion Theme Package ===\n\n?? rainmeter-skins\n?? wallpapers\n   ?? install.ps1 (6.8 KB)\n   ?? README.md (2.6 KB)\n   ?? set-wallpaper.ps1 (0.8 KB)\n   ?? Wallpaper.cs (0.3 KB)\n?? NotionStyle\n   ?? NotionStyle-Light.ini (3.9 KB)\n   ?? NotionStyle.ini (4.4 KB)\n   ?? notion-dark.png (17.5 KB)\n   ?? notion-gradient.png (99.8 KB)\n   ?? notion-light.png (17.5 KB)\n\nTotal size: 0.15 MB"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1048,"aggregated":"=== Notion Theme Package ===\n\n?? rainmeter-skins\n?? wallpapers\n   ?? install.ps1 (6.8 KB)\n   ?? README.md (2.6 KB)\n   ?? set-wallpaper.ps1 (0.8 KB)\n   ?? Wallpaper.cs (0.3 KB)\n?? NotionStyle\n   ?? NotionStyle-Light.ini (3.9 KB)\n   ?? NotionStyle.ini (4.4 KB)\n   ?? notion-dark.png (17.5 KB)\n   ?? notion-gradient.png (99.8 KB)\n   ?? notion-light.png (17.5 KB)\n\nTotal size: 0.15 MB","cwd":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773579279540}}
{"type":"message","id":"d4af27ab","parentId":"650a0999","timestamp":"2026-03-15T12:54:48.203Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"一切就绪！现在让我给用户一个清晰的总结。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## ✅ Notion 风格主题包已完成！\n\n**桌面上的 `Notion-Theme` 文件夹包含：**\n\n| 项目 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| 🖼️ 深色壁纸 | ✅ 已应用 |\n| 🎨 Rainmeter 皮肤 (深/浅两版) | ✅ 已创建 |\n| 📋 安装脚本 | ✅ 已就绪 |\n| 📖 使用说明 | ✅ README.md |\n\n---\n\n### 🔧 还需要你手动安装：\n\n**1. Rainmeter** → [官网下载](https://www.rainmeter.net/)\n```powershell\n# 安装后运行此命令加载皮肤\n.\\install.ps1 -InstallRainmeterSkin\n```\n\n**2. TranslucentTB** → [GitHub 下载](https://github.com/TranslucentTB/TranslucentTB/releases)\n- 安装后在托盘选择 \"Clear\" 让任务栏透明\n\n---\n\n### 🎯 装完 Rainmeter 后：\n\n1. 右键托盘图标 → **管理皮肤**\n2. 左侧找到 `NotionStyle`\n3. 展开 → 加载 `NotionStyle.ini`\n4. 拖动到桌面左上角合适位置\n\n---\n\n**壁纸已切换为深色 Notion 风格，现在去看看你的桌面！** 🖤\n\n想浅色版的话运行：\n```powershell\n.\\set-wallpaper.ps1 -Theme light\n```"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":446,"output":334,"cacheRead":27968,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28748,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773579279542}}
