{"type":"message","id":"3ebec7a1","parentId":"8e887e28","timestamp":"2026-03-15T12:57:08.765Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想让我直接帮他完成安装。之前的网络问题导致无法自动下载 Rainmeter 和 TranslucentTB。让我再试一次，或者尝试其他方式安装这些软件。\n\n我可以：\n1. 再试一次下载\n2. 尝试使用其他下载源\n3. 手动创建一个批处理脚本让用户运行\n\n让我再尝试下载，这次用更可靠的方式。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，让我再试一次完整安装："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf19251f64ea819c3d5d4634f20e2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 尝试使用 BITS 服务下载（更可靠）\n$themeDir = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\"\n\nWrite-Host \"=== 安装 Rainmeter ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n\n# 使用 Start-BitsTransfer（Windows 内置，更可靠）\n$rainmeterUrl = \"https://github.com/rainmeter/rainmeter/releases/download/v4.5.18.3762/Rainmeter-4.5.18.3762.exe\"\n$rainmeterPath = \"$themeDir\\rainmeter.exe\"\n\ntry {\n    Start-BitsTransfer -Source $rainmeterUrl -Destination $rainmeterPath -ErrorAction Stop\n    Write-Host \"[OK] Rainmeter 下载成功\" -ForegroundColor Green\n    \n    # 自动运行安装\n    Write-Host \"正在启动安装程序...\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n    Start-Process -FilePath $rainmeterPath -ArgumentList \"/S\" -Wait\n    Write-Host \"[OK] Rainmeter 安装完成\" -ForegroundColor Green\n} catch {\n    Write-Host \"[ERROR] 下载失败: $_\" -ForegroundColor Red\n}","timeout":300}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":12491,"output":411,"cacheRead":16000,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28902,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773579413361}}
