{"type":"message","id":"b1cb366b","parentId":"8535549a","timestamp":"2026-03-15T12:58:08.653Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Rainmeter installed successfully! Now let me install TranslucentTB and then configure everything.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Rainmeter 安装成功！继续安装 TranslucentTB："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf19335207600ff9d45605bfa9966","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 下载并安装 TranslucentTB\n$themeDir = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\"\n\nWrite-Host \"=== 下载 TranslucentTB ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n\n$tbUrl = \"https://github.com/TranslucentTB/TranslucentTB/releases/download/2024.1/TranslucentTB.Setup.exe\"\n$tbPath = \"$themeDir\\translucenttb-setup.exe\"\n\ntry {\n    Invoke-WebRequest -Uri $tbUrl -OutFile $tbPath -UseBasicParsing -TimeoutSec 60\n    Write-Host \"[OK] 下载成功!\" -ForegroundColor Green\n} catch {\n    # 尝试备用链接\n    $tbUrl2 = \"https://downloads.sourceforge.net/project/translucenttb/TranslucentTB/2024.1/TranslucentTB.Setup.exe\"\n    try {\n        Invoke-WebRequest -Uri $tbUrl2 -OutFile $tbPath -UseBasicParsing -TimeoutSec 60\n        Write-Host \"[OK] 下载成功!\" -ForegroundColor Green\n    } catch {\n        Write-Host \"[ERROR] 无法下载，请手动安装\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n        Write-Host \"Store: ms-windows-store://pdp/?PFN=28017CharlesMilette.TranslucentTB\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n    }\n}\n\nif (Test-Path $tbPath) {\n    Write-Host \"安装中...\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n    Start-Process -FilePath $tbPath -ArgumentList \"/silent\" -Wait\n    Write-Host \"[OK] TranslucentTB 安装完成!\" -ForegroundColor Green\n}","timeout":180}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":572,"output":390,"cacheRead":28800,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29762,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773579475418}}
{"type":"message","id":"fe450e72","parentId":"b1cb366b","timestamp":"2026-03-15T12:58:19.895Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019cf19335207600ff9d45605bfa9966","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== ���� TranslucentTB ===\n[OK] ���سɹ�!\n��װ��...\nStart-Process : ���ڳ������´����޷����д�����: �ļ���Ŀ¼�����޷���ȡ����\r\n����λ�� ��:26 �ַ�: 5\r\n+     Start-Process -FilePath $tbPath -ArgumentList \"/silent\" -Wait\r\n+     ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\r\n    + CategoryInfo          : InvalidOperation: (:) [Start-Process]��InvalidOperationException\r\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : InvalidOperationException,Microsoft.PowerShell.Commands.StartProcessCommand\r\n \r\n[OK] TranslucentTB ��װ���!"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":11235,"aggregated":"=== ���� TranslucentTB ===\n[OK] ���سɹ�!\n��װ��...\nStart-Process : ���ڳ������´����޷����д�����: �ļ���Ŀ¼�����޷���ȡ����\r\n����λ�� ��:26 �ַ�: 5\r\n+     Start-Process -FilePath $tbPath -ArgumentList \"/silent\" -Wait\r\n+     ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\r\n    + CategoryInfo          : InvalidOperation: (:) [Start-Process]��InvalidOperationException\r\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : InvalidOperationException,Microsoft.PowerShell.Commands.StartProcessCommand\r\n \r\n[OK] TranslucentTB ��װ���!","cwd":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773579499893}}
{"type":"message","id":"aca6669b","parentId":"fe450e72","timestamp":"2026-03-15T12:58:28.765Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"TranslucentTB downloaded but the silent install didn't work properly. Let me check if it's installed, and if not, try a different approach. Let me also install the Rainmeter skins and start everything.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf1938817975e32eaa33e72640ac5","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查已安装的程序\nWrite-Host \"=== 检查已安装软件 ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n\n$rainmeter = Get-ItemProperty \"HKLM:\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Uninstall\\*\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | \n              Where-Object { $_.DisplayName -like \"*Rainmeter*\" }\nif ($rainmeter) {\n    Write-Host \"[OK] Rainmeter 已安装\" -ForegroundColor Green\n    $rainmeterPath = \"C:\\Program Files\\Rainmeter\\Rainmeter.exe\"\n    if (Test-Path $rainmeterPath) {\n        Write-Host \"    路径: $rainmeterPath\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n    }\n} else {\n    Write-Host \"[X] Rainmeter 未找到\" -ForegroundColor Red\n}\n\n$tb = Get-ItemProperty \"HKLM:\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Uninstall\\*\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | \n      Where-Object { $_.DisplayName -like \"*Translucent*\" }\nif ($tb) {\n    Write-Host \"[OK] TranslucentTB 已安装\" -ForegroundColor Green\n} else {\n    Write-Host \"[I] TranslucentTB 需要手动安装\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n    Write-Host \"    双击运行: $env:USERPROFILE\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\translucenttb-setup.exe\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":581,"output":389,"cacheRead":29312,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30282,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773579499895}}
{"type":"message","id":"e5e4cb4a","parentId":"aca6669b","timestamp":"2026-03-15T12:58:30.039Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019cf1938817975e32eaa33e72640ac5","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== ����Ѱ�װ���� ===\n[X] Rainmeter δ�ҵ�\n[I] TranslucentTB ��Ҫ�ֶ���װ\n    ˫������: C:\\Users\\16343\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\translucenttb-setup.exe"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1269,"aggregated":"=== ����Ѱ�װ���� ===\n[X] Rainmeter δ�ҵ�\n[I] TranslucentTB ��Ҫ�ֶ���װ\n    ˫������: C:\\Users\\16343\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\translucenttb-setup.exe","cwd":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773579510038}}
{"type":"message","id":"b109dfdb","parentId":"e5e4cb4a","timestamp":"2026-03-15T12:58:46.078Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Rainmeter was downloaded but seems not installed via the silent installer, or it might be installed in a different location. Let me check the user's AppData and Program Files more thoroughly. Also, let me run the Rainmeter installer manually.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf193cc151a44ebd272675b7d97c9","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查 Rainmeter 是否在其他位置\nWrite-Host \"查找 Rainmeter...\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n\n$locations = @(\n    \"$env:LOCALAPPDATA\\Rainmeter\",\n    \"$env:APPDATA\\Rainmeter\",\n    \"${env:ProgramFiles(x86)}\\Rainmeter\",\n    \"$env:ProgramFiles\\Rainmeter\"\n)\n\nforeach ($loc in $locations) {\n    if (Test-Path $loc) {\n        Write-Host \"[OK] 找到: $loc\" -ForegroundColor Green\n    }\n}\n\n# 检查是否有 Rainmeter 进程\n$process = Get-Process -Name \"Rainmeter\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nif ($process) {\n    Write-Host \"[OK] Rainmeter 正在运行!\" -ForegroundColor Green\n}\n\n# 直接运行安装程序（交互式）\nWrite-Host \"`n启动 Rainmeter 安装程序...\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n$installer = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\rainmeter-setup.exe\"\nif (Test-Path $installer) {\n    Start-Process -FilePath $installer\n    Write-Host \"[OK] 安装程序已启动，请按照向导完成安装\" -ForegroundColor Green\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":415,"output":358,"cacheRead":29888,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30661,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773579510040}}
{"type":"message","id":"404626dc","parentId":"b109dfdb","timestamp":"2026-03-15T12:58:47.198Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019cf193cc151a44ebd272675b7d97c9","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"���� Rainmeter...\n[OK] �ҵ�: C:\\Program Files\\Rainmeter\n\n���� Rainmeter ��װ����...\n[OK] ��װ�������������밴������ɰ�װ"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1117,"aggregated":"���� Rainmeter...\n[OK] �ҵ�: C:\\Program Files\\Rainmeter\n\n���� Rainmeter ��װ����...\n[OK] ��װ�������������밴������ɰ�װ","cwd":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773579527197}}
{"type":"message","id":"78bb91f5","parentId":"404626dc","timestamp":"2026-03-15T12:59:00.202Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Rainmeter is actually installed in C:\\Program Files\\Rainmeter. The registry check might have missed it because it's installed differently. Let me proceed with copying the skins and starting Rainmeter.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Rainmeter 已安装！现在部署皮肤并启动："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf193f14335aca8f05050fbb7efbf","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 复制皮肤到 Rainmeter 目录\n$skinSource = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\rainmeter-skins\\NotionStyle\"\n$skinDest = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\Documents\\Rainmeter\\Skins\\NotionStyle\"\n\nWrite-Host \"=== 安装 Notion 皮肤 ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n\n# 确保目标目录存在\n$skinsRoot = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\Documents\\Rainmeter\\Skins\"\nif (-not (Test-Path $skinsRoot)) {\n    New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $skinsRoot -Force | Out-Null\n}\n\n# 复制皮肤\nif (Test-Path $skinDest) {\n    Remove-Item $skinDest -Recurse -Force\n}\nCopy-Item $skinSource -Destination $skinDest -Recurse -Force\nWrite-Host \"[OK] 皮肤已复制到: $skinDest\" -ForegroundColor Green\n\n# 创建 Rainmeter 设置文件来自动加载皮肤\n$settingsPath = \"$env:APPDATA\\Rainmeter\\Rainmeter.ini\"\n$settingsContent = @\"\n[Rainmeter]\nSkinPath=$skinsRoot\\\nDefault=\"\\#SKINSPATH#\\#Config#\\\"\n\n[NotionStyle\\NotionStyle]\nActive=1\nLeft=20\nTop=20\n\"@\n\n# 备份现有设置\nif (Test-Path $settingsPath) {\n    Copy-Item $settingsPath \"$settingsPath.backup\" -Force\n    Write-Host \"[OK] 已备份现有设置\" -ForegroundColor Green\n}\n\n# 写入新设置\n$settingsContent | Out-File -FilePath $settingsPath -Encoding Unicode -Force\nWrite-Host \"[OK] 已配置 Rainmeter 设置\" -ForegroundColor Green\n\n# 启动 Rainmeter\nWrite-Host \"`n=== 启动 Rainmeter ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n$rainmeterExe = \"C:\\Program Files\\Rainmeter\\Rainmeter.exe\"\nif (Test-Path $rainmeterExe) {\n    # 先关闭可能运行的实例\n    Get-Process -Name \"Rainmeter\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Stop-Process -Force\n    Start-Sleep -Seconds 1\n    \n    # 启动 Rainmeter\n    Start-Process -FilePath $rainmeterExe\n    Write-Host \"[OK] Rainmeter 已启动!\" -ForegroundColor Green\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":393,"output":596,"cacheRead":30272,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31261,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773579527199}}
