{"type":"message","id":"ae2d8ae5","parentId":"57017b9b","timestamp":"2026-03-15T12:59:31.692Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The TranslucentTB setup file is very small (0.06 MB), which suggests it might be a stub/launcher that downloads the actual installer. The error \"文件或目录损坏且无法读取\" means the file might be corrupted or incomplete.\n\nLet me try opening the Microsoft Store instead, which is more reliable for Windows 10/11.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"TranslucentTB 安装包可能不完整。让我从 Microsoft Store 安装："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf19477958b288a458b6f85f67ffd","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 从 Microsoft Store 安装 TranslucentTB\nWrite-Host \"=== 从 Microsoft Store 安装 TranslucentTB ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host \"正在打开 Store...\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n\nStart-Process \"ms-windows-store://pdp/?PFN=28017CharlesMilette.TranslucentTB\"\nWrite-Host \"[OK] Microsoft Store 已打开\" -ForegroundColor Green\nWrite-Host \"    请点击'获取'安装 TranslucentTB\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n\n# 创建快速启动脚本供后续使用\n$quickStart = @\"\n@echo off\necho === Notion Theme 快速设置 ===\necho.\necho 1. 启用任务栏透明 (需要 TranslucentTB)\necho 2. 切换深色壁纸\necho 3. 切换浅色壁纸\necho.\nchoice /c 123 /n /m \"选择: \"\n\nif errorlevel 3 (\n    powershell -File \"$env:USERPROFILE\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\set-wallpaper.ps1\" -Theme light\n)\nif errorlevel 2 (\n    powershell -File \"$env:USERPROFILE\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\set-wallpaper.ps1\" -Theme dark\n)\nif errorlevel 1 (\n    start \"\" \"C:\\Program Files\\TranslucentTB\\TranslucentTB.exe\"\n    timeout /t 2 /nobreak >nul\n)\n\"@\n\n$quickStart | Out-File -FilePath \"$env:USERPROFILE\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\quick-menu.bat\" -Encoding ASCII\nWrite-Host \"`n[OK] 已创建快速菜单: quick-menu.bat\" -ForegroundColor Green"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":462,"output":504,"cacheRead":31808,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32774,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773579561199}}
