{"type":"message","id":"baa888df","parentId":"27c86e1b","timestamp":"2026-03-15T13:04:00.027Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK there were some encoding issues but the commands succeeded. Let me provide a summary for the user.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n## 🎉 Notion 风格美化已完成！\n\n### 已完成的设置：\n\n| 项目 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| 🖼️ 深色壁纸 | ✅ 已应用 |\n| 🌙 系统深色模式 | ✅ 已启用 |\n| 🪟 透明效果 | ✅ 已开启 |\n| 🎨 Rainmeter | ✅ 已启动 |\n| 📋 NotionStyle 皮肤 | ✅ 已加载 |\n| 🚀 开机自启 | ✅ 已设置 |\n\n### 还需要你操作：\n\n**TranslucentTB（任务栏透明）：**\n- Microsoft Store 应该已经打开了\n- 点击「**获取**」按钮安装\n- 安装后右键托盘图标 → 选择 **Clear**\n\n---\n\n**现在看看你的桌面！** \n\n左上角应该有：\n- ⏰ 大号时间显示\n- 📅 日期\n- 📋 待办清单\n- ⚡ 快捷方式\n\n皮肤文件位置（可自定义内容）：\n```\nC:\\Users\\16343\\Documents\\Rainmeter\\Skins\\NotionStyle\\NotionStyle.ini\n```\n\n---\n\n还想调整什么？比如：\n- 改变位置/大小\n- 修改待办内容\n- 添加更多快捷方式\n- 换成浅色主题"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":1101,"output":325,"cacheRead":35520,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36946,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773579827898}}
