{"type":"message","id":"8509158d","parentId":"27c66034","timestamp":"2026-03-15T13:19:38.859Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来壁纸设置对了，Rainmeter正在运行，皮肤文件存在，配置也正确。但用户说没看到变化。\n\n可能问题：\n1. 壁纸虽然设置了，但没有刷新生效\n2. Rainmeter皮肤没有正确加载\n3. 皮肤本身有bug，不显示\n\n让我尝试强制刷新，并且直接操作来确保一切正常。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"配置看起来是对的，让我强制刷新所有效果："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf1a6db57b5475af8874c42ee9e00","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 强制刷新所有效果\nWrite-Host \"=== 强制刷新 ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n\n# 1. 强制刷新壁纸\nWrite-Host \"`n刷新壁纸...\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\nAdd-Type @\"\nusing System;\nusing System.Runtime.InteropServices;\npublic class WP {\n    [DllImport(\"user32.dll\")]\n    public static extern int SystemParametersInfo(int a, int b, string c, int d);\n}\n\"@\n\n$wallpaperPath = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\wallpapers\\notion-dark.png\"\n[WP]::SystemParametersInfo(20, 0, $wallpaperPath, 3)\nWrite-Host \"[OK] 壁纸已刷新\" -ForegroundColor Green\n\n# 2. 重启 Rainmeter 并加载皮肤\nWrite-Host \"`n重启 Rainmeter...\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\nGet-Process -Name \"Rainmeter\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Stop-Process -Force\nStart-Sleep -Seconds 1\n\n$rmExe = \"C:\\Program Files\\Rainmeter\\Rainmeter.exe\"\nif (Test-Path $rmExe) {\n    Start-Process $rmExe\n    Start-Sleep -Seconds 3\n    Write-Host \"[OK] Rainmeter 已重启\" -ForegroundColor Green\n    \n    # 强制加载皮肤\n    & $rmExe \"!ActivateConfig\" \"NotionStyle\\NotionStyle\"\n    Start-Sleep -Seconds 1\n    & $rmExe \"!Redraw\"\n    Write-Host \"[OK] 皮肤已强制加载\" -ForegroundColor Green\n}\n\n# 3. 刷新桌面\nWrite-Host \"`n刷新桌面...\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\nStop-Process -Name \"explorer\" -Force\nStart-Sleep -Seconds 2\nStart-Process \"explorer.exe\"\nWrite-Host \"[OK] 桌面已刷新\" -ForegroundColor Green\n\nWrite-Host \"`n完成! 等待桌面重新加载...\" -ForegroundColor Cyan","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":624,"output":587,"cacheRead":36800,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38011,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773580763293}}
