{"type":"message","id":"282546bb","parentId":"56e7b130","timestamp":"2026-03-15T13:20:05.925Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我做了以下操作：\n1. 强制刷新壁纸\n2. 重启 Rainmeter\n3. 强制加载 NotionStyle 皮肤\n4. 重启 Explorer 来刷新桌面\n\n现在让用户确认是否看到变化。如果还是没有，可能是皮肤本身的问题，我需要检查皮肤文件格式或者创建一个更简单的测试皮肤。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf1a73f4882f8b0a8bf200dfe9ba7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 等待桌面加载完成，然后检查\nStart-Sleep -Seconds 3\n\nWrite-Host \"=== 最终检查 ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n\n# 检查 Rainmeter 皮肤状态\n$rmExe = \"C:\\Program Files\\Rainmeter\\Rainmeter.exe\"\n\n# 列出所有已加载的皮肤\nWrite-Host \"`n已加载的皮肤:\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n& $rmExe \"!Log\" \"Checking skins\"\n\n# 尝试更直接的方式加载皮肤\nWrite-Host \"直接加载皮肤到屏幕...\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n& $rmExe \"!ActivateConfig\" \"NotionStyle\\NotionStyle\" \"NotionStyle.ini\"\n\n# 也创建一个极简测试皮肤确保能显示\n$testSkin = @\"\n[Rainmeter]\nUpdate=1000\nAccurateText=1\nDynamicWindowSize=1\n\n[MeterTime]\nMeter=String\nX=0\nY=0\nFontFace=Microsoft YaHei UI\nFontSize=72\nFontColor=255,255,255,255\nStringAlign=Left\nAntiAlias=1\nMeasureName=MeasureTime\n\n[MeasureTime]\nMeasure=Time\nFormat=%H:%M\n\n[MeterDate]\nMeter=String\nMeasureName=MeasureDate\nX=0\nY=80\nFontFace=Microsoft YaHei UI\nFontSize=24\nFontColor=200,200,200,255\nAntiAlias=1\n\n[MeasureDate]\nMeasure=Time\nFormat=%A, %B %d\n\"@\n\n$testSkinPath = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\Documents\\Rainmeter\\Skins\\NotionStyle\\Test.ini\"\n$testSkin | Out-File -FilePath $testSkinPath -Encoding UTF8\nWrite-Host \"[OK] 测试皮肤已创建\" -ForegroundColor Green\n\n# 刷新并加载测试皮肤\n& $rmExe \"!Refresh\"\nStart-Sleep -Milliseconds 500\n& $rmExe \"!DeactivateConfig\" \"NotionStyle\\NotionStyle\"\n& $rmExe \"!ActivateConfig\" \"NotionStyle\\Test\"\nWrite-Host \"[OK] 测试皮肤已加载\" -ForegroundColor Green\n\nWrite-Host \"`n现在应该能在桌面看到大号时间显示了！\" -ForegroundColor Cyan"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":643,"outpu