{"type":"message","id":"4d34fed8","parentId":"45e5d0c6","timestamp":"2026-03-15T19:54:27.470Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说没有生效，需要再尝试一下。同时用户要求整理桌面，删除快捷启动图标。\n\n让我：\n1. 再次检查并强制设置壁纸\n2. 重新加载 Rainmeter 皮肤\n3. 清理桌面上的快捷方式图标","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，让我重新来一遍并整理桌面："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf3105b9ca80f64feee7340187e13","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 清理桌面快捷方式\nWrite-Host \"=== 清理桌面快捷方式 ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n\n$desktopPath = [Environment]::GetFolderPath(\"Desktop\")\nWrite-Host \"桌面路径: $desktopPath\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n\n# 获取桌面上的所有快捷方式\n$shortcuts = Get-ChildItem -Path $desktopPath -Filter \"*.lnk\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nWrite-Host \"找到 $($shortcuts.Count) 个快捷方式\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n\n# 删除快捷方式（保留 Notion-Theme 文件夹）\nforeach ($shortcut in $shortcuts) {\n    $name = $shortcut.Name\n    Write-Host \"  删除: $name\" -ForegroundColor DarkGray\n    Remove-Item $shortcut.FullName -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n}\n\n# 也检查其他桌面位置\n$publicDesktop = \"C:\\Users\\Public\\Desktop\"\nif (Test-Path $publicDesktop) {\n    $publicShortcuts = Get-ChildItem -Path $publicDesktop -Filter \"*.lnk\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n    foreach ($sc in $publicShortcuts) {\n        Write-Host \"  删除公共桌面: $($sc.Name)\" -ForegroundColor DarkGray\n        Remove-Item $sc.FullName -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n    }\n}\n\nWrite-Host \"[OK] 快捷方式已清理\" -ForegroundColor Green\n\n# 列出桌面剩余内容\nWrite-Host \"`n桌面剩余内容:\" -ForegroundColor White\nGet-ChildItem $desktopPath | ForEach-Object {\n    Write-Host \"  $($_.Name)\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":30649,"output":464,"cacheRead":8064,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39177,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773604455931}}
