{"type":"message","id":"80755cf4","parentId":"6bdeb971","timestamp":"2026-03-15T19:55:24.484Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来设置已经完成了，但用户说没有生效。让我尝试更直接的方式 - 也许需要用户手动确认或者截图看看效果。也可能是显示器刷新或者 Windows 某些设置阻止了更改。\n\n让我再尝试一种不同的方法来确保更改生效。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"配置都正确了，让我用另一种方式强制刷新："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf31136754f584f52d965044f82a4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 使用更强的方式刷新\nWrite-Host \"=== 强制系统刷新 ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n\n# 1. 重启 explorer 进程\nWrite-Host \"重启桌面...\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\nStop-Process -Name \"explorer\" -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nStart-Sleep -Seconds 2\n\n# 2. 确保 Rainmeter 随后启动\n$rmExe = \"C:\\Program Files\\Rainmeter\\Rainmeter.exe\"\nStart-Process \"explorer.exe\"\nStart-Sleep -Seconds 3\n\nif (Test-Path $rmExe) {\n    # 先停止，再启动\n    Get-Process -Name \"Rainmeter\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Stop-Process -Force\n    Start-Sleep -Seconds 1\n    Start-Process $rmExe\n    Start-Sleep -Seconds 2\n    Write-Host \"[OK] Rainmeter 重启完成\" -ForegroundColor Green\n}\n\n# 3. 检查是否有 Rainmeter 窗口\n$rmWindow = Get-Process -Name \"Rainmeter\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nif ($rmWindow) {\n    Write-Host \"[OK] Rainmeter 进程 PID: $($rmWindow.Id)\" -ForegroundColor Green\n    \n    # 发送刷新命令\n    & $rmExe \"!RefreshApp\"\n    & $rmExe \"!ActivateConfig\" \"NotionStyle\" \"NotionStyle.ini\"\n}\n\nWrite-Host \"`n=== 完成 ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host \"请检查桌面是否有变化\" -ForegroundColor White\nWrite-Host \"- 壁纸应该是深黑色\" -ForegroundColor Gray\nWrite-Host \"- 左上角应该有大号时间显示\" -ForegroundColor Gray"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":583,"output":489,"cacheRead":40896,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41968,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773604512621}}
