{"type":"message","id":"49f1c38e","parentId":"19c03648","timestamp":"2026-03-15T19:55:47.814Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说还是没有生效。让我想想可能的问题：\n\n1. 壁纸可能是黑色的一眼看不出来变化\n2. Rainmeter 皮肤可能没有正确显示在桌面上\n\n我应该问问用户具体看到了什么。或者我可以帮助他们确认一些事情。让我检查是否有其他问题。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf3119100166d84211cf82a73d126","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查更多信息来诊断问题\nWrite-Host \"=== 诊断检查 ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n\n# 1. 检查壁纸文件是否正确\n$wpFile = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\Desktop\\Notion-Theme\\wallpapers\\notion-dark.png\"\nif (Test-Path $wpFile) {\n    $file = Get-Item $wpFile\n    Write-Host \"[OK] 壁纸文件存在: $($file.Length) bytes\" -ForegroundColor Green\n} else {\n    Write-Host \"[X] 壁纸文件不存在!\" -ForegroundColor Red\n}\n\n# 2. 检查屏幕分辨率\nAdd-Type -AssemblyName System.Windows.Forms\n$screen = [System.Windows.Forms.Screen]::PrimaryScreen\nWrite-Host \"`n屏幕分辨率: $($screen.Bounds.Width)x$($screen.Bounds.Height)\" -ForegroundColor White\n\n# 3. 检查 Rainmeter 日志\nWrite-Host \"`nRainmeter 日志 (最后几行):\" -ForegroundColor White\n$logPath = \"$env:APPDATA\\Rainmeter\\Rainmeter.log\"\nif (Test-Path $logPath) {\n    Get-Content $logPath -Tail 10 -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n}\n\n# 4. 列出 Rainmeter 皮肤目录内容\nWrite-Host \"`n皮肤目录内容:\" -ForegroundColor White\n$skinPath = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\Documents\\Rainmeter\\Skins\\NotionStyle\"\nif (Test-Path $skinPath) {\n    Get-ChildItem $skinPath | ForEach-Object { Write-Host \"  $($_.Name)\" -ForegroundColor Gray }\n}\n\n# 5. 检查配置文件\nWrite-Host \"`nRainmeter.ini 内容:\" -ForegroundColor White\nGet-Content \"$env:APPDATA\\Rainmeter\\Rainmeter.ini\" | Select-Object -First 15"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"siliconflow","model":"Pro/zai-org/GLM-5","usage":{"input":522,"output":518,"cacheRead":41472,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42512,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773604533841}}
